data.description: Yorkville! Welcome to 512 Sinclair Ave! This move in ready 2 BR 2 BA home sits comfortably on a corner lot and has already had several updates! It boasts replacement windows throughout that carry a lifetime warranty. The furnace and air conditioner brought additional ductwork and are less than 5 years old. All appliances stay including extra cold storage located in the full basement. Relax on your covered front porch while you decide on how you'll make this home your own!!!
